race.description: Great Western Insurance Ladies Day Sprint Hcp
race.comment: Tough race with many chances. ONEMORETWOMANY (2) showed real fight fresh when holding a forward spot and only fading late. Fitter for that and finds an easier race this time. Draw makes things tricky but with a clean getaway he can take catching. Looks ready to peak. DIVINE INANNA (5) hit her straps third up with a stylish win here, cruising past them with plenty in hand. Carries a bit more weight but clearly trending the right way. Hard to knock and rates a major hope again. LOVA SESSION (3) rarely runs poorly and strips fitter second up after a solid return in stronger company. With the claim and a touch of luck in running, she's a threat. SURE NO SOMETHING (1) is a local marvel who loves this track and always gives his all. Big weight but class will carry him close. COLLECTIVE (4) is another track specialist resuming and must be included.
